##Architectural analysis of FastAi library

At the very base of FastAi we have the _ItemBase_ class.
The _**ItemBase**_ child classes are telling what type of problems we can solve in FastAi.

<img src=" data:image/png;base64," />

As you may see you can work with text, single or multi-label classification, tabular data, regression (floats), images...

The very base is `ItemBase`, but the lists are inside `ItemLists` class.
There should be an `ItemList` for each of `train` and `valid` and optional `test` set.
For instance if we have 1000 images in the train set and 100 images, info on these images should be inside the lists.
